  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.poster.avif?t=1701924186\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.webm?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.mp4?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bean Climb - A hard torture during a dark night. You are a bean that got intentionally thrown out of a jelly bean packet. You're not going to give up right? It's time to overcome all the hard obstacles that you will face, it's not going to be easy, at times you are gonna feel unmotivated, but you have to do it...<br><br>You may ask, why? Why overcome the obstacles? Well, while sweating and climbing, the bean will explain everything to you :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Chargeable jump</strong></li></ul>Charge your jump according to how far, or how high you have to jump.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No air control</strong></li></ul>Remember you're just a bean, you're barely moving on the ground, so forget about moving mid-air.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Careful on the steep slopes</strong></li></ul>Do you still remember that you are just a bean? Because steep slopes, will make you slide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/78635461af55e5b01ffd399c12472e1f.poster.avif?t=1701924186\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/78635461af55e5b01ffd399c12472e1f.webm?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/78635461af55e5b01ffd399c12472e1f.mp4?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>By the way, I believe in you! You can do it! You may sweat, you may cry, but you got this!</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.poster.avif?t=1701924186\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.webm?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/8953a18eb26637e374cfc87e8340246a.mp4?t=1701924186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bean Climb - A hard torture during a dark night. You are a bean that got intentionally thrown out of a jelly bean packet. You're not going to give up right? It's time to overcome all the hard obstacles that you will face, it's not going to be easy, at times you are gonna feel unmotivated, but you have to do it...<br><br>You may ask, why? Why overcome the obstacles? Well, while sweating and climbing, the bean will explain everything to you :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Chargeable jump</strong></li></ul>Charge your jump according to how far, or how high you have to jump.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No air control</strong></li></ul>Remember you're just a bean, you're barely moving on the ground, so forget about moving mid-air.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Careful on the steep slopes</strong></li></ul>Do you still remember that you are just a bean? Because steep slopes, will make you slide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/78635461af55e5b01ffd399c12472e1f.poster.avif?t=1701924186\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411000/extras/78635461af55e5b